snippet.title: Swift Fun Algorithms: Retain Cycle Correction!
snippet.description:
Apologies for a mistake I made in last week's video about how to create a retain cycle.  Today's video we'll discuss the proper way to introduce our reference cycle inside our program.  Please make sure to go over this exercise again to see the difference.
